<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>464</hymn_number>
<key>F</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Keimah misual caah Bawi Jesuh a thi cang, Nuntlak lo ka thlarau khamh
 awkah, Vai-lamtah lam har kha, Keimah ruangah a zulh, Ka sualnak vialte
 ngaihthiam awkah.

[C1]
   Ka sualnak vialte kha vailam ah an khenh chih, Zeitluk in dah
   sifahnak a in? Ngaihchiat phun zakip he Jesuh Kal-va-ry ah Ka sual vialte
   a kalpi dih cang.

[V2]
 Dawt tlak lo kei cungah hin a thin a fual i Ka lungthin thur kha a ka
 tawl cang, Thangchia mualpho tel loin, Keimah ka luat cang, Ka sual
 vailam ah an khenh chih cang.

[C2]
   Ka sualnak vialte kha vailam ah an khenh chih, Zeitluk in dah
   sifahnak a in? Ngaihchiat phun zakip he Jesuh Kal-va-ry ah Ka sual vialte
   a kalpi dih cang.

[V3]
 Ka sualnak kha a ka lakpiak dih cang tiin, Ka lungthin chung le ka
 hmur-ka in. Lawmhnak hla he ka Khamhbawi cu ka thangthat lai, Amah cu ka
 zulh zungzal ko lai.

[C3]
   Ka sualnak vialte kha vailam ah an khenh chih, Zeitluk in dah
   sifahnak a in? Ngaihchiat phun zakip he Jesuh Kal-va-ry ah Ka sual vialte
   a kalpi dih cang.</lyrics>
<title>VAILAM AH AN KHENH CHIH CH464</title>
</song>